OL,3,CIsrael weaponising pager will rattle
OL,4,CHezbollah - but when will they strike
OL,5,Cback?
OL,7,FIt comes amid rising tensions between
OL,8,FIsrael and Hezbollah, who have
OL,9,Fexchanged fire across the Israel-
OL,10,FLebanon border since the October 7
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FThe Israelis cracked Hezbollah's code.
OL,15,FSecurity services that managed the
OL,16,Fincredible feat of turning pagers into
OL,17,Fbombs would almost certainly have been
OL,18,Fprivy to the messages that appeared on
OL,19,Fthose devices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
