OL,3,CIsrael weaponising pager will rattle
OL,4,CHezbollah - but when will they strike
OL,5,Cback?
OL,7,FAs we know from Bletchley Park during
OL,8,FWorld War II, it is a huge asset to be
OL,9,Fable to eavesdrop on your adversary's
OL,10,Fcommunications.
OL,12,FI can think of only two reasons why
OL,13,Fyou would deliberately blow the whole
OL,14,Fthing up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
