OL,3,CIsrael weaponising pager will rattle
OL,4,CHezbollah - but when will they strike
OL,5,Cback?
OL,7,FThe Israelis pushed the button to
OL,8,Fdestroy Hezbollah's command and
OL,9,Fcontrol bleeper network either because
OL,10,Fthey are about to launch a big
OL,11,Foffensive into south Lebanon, or,
OL,12,Fbecause they feared their secret
OL,13,Finfiltration of the pager system had
OL,14,Fbeen uncovered, and they may as well
OL,15,Fclose down the operation with a
OL,16,Fdecisive strike against hundreds of
OL,17,Foperatives.
OL,19,FOn Wednesday morning, reputable
OL,20,FIsraeli journalists are suggesting the
OL,21,Freason was the latter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
